OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783779570
OL,3,CDolphins join RNLI volunteers during
OL,4,Ctraining exercise
OL,6,FA crew from Littlehampton RNLI were
OL,7,Fdelighted when a pod of dolphins
OL,8,Fjoined them on a training exercise off
OL,9,Fthe West Sussex Coast.
OL,11,FThe routine exercise turned into a
OL,12,Fbucket-list moment for the volunteer
OL,13,Fcrew when dolphins began leaping
OL,14,Faround them.
OL,16,FHelm Andy Harris and crew Sophie
OL,17,FCollins, Ian Kirkham and Mark Jordan
OL,18,Fwere on their regular Thursday (9
OL,19,FJuly) evening training exercise off
OL,20,Fthe coast of Littlehampton when they
OL,21,Fspotted dolphins ahead.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
