OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783779570
OL,3,CDolphins join RNLI volunteers during
OL,4,Ctraining exercise
OL,6,FTheir lifeboat was suddenly surrounded
OL,7,Fby the inquisitive pod, which included
OL,8,Fa mother and calf.
OL,10,FThe dolphins stayed with the crew for
OL,11,Fabout 10 minutes, leaping out of the
OL,12,Fsea and playing in the lifeboat's wake.
OL,14,FSophie Collins, who joined
OL,15,FLittlehampton RNLI in August 2024 and
OL,16,Frecently passed out as crew, said: "It
OL,17,Fwas literally the best day of my life.
OL,19,F"It was such a peaceful sight and the
OL,20,Fperfect way to end our evening
OL,21,Ftraining session."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
