FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783779570
OL,3,CDolphins join RNLI volunteers during
OL,4,Ctraining exercise
OL,6,FAndy Harris, who was at the helm and
OL,7,Fhas volunteered with Littlehampton
OL,8,FRNLI since 1996, said: "It's one of
OL,9,Fthose sights you never get tired of
OL,10,Fseeing.
OL,12,F"We saw them ahead, then we saw
OL,13,Fanother group coming up behind us.
OL,15,F"They came to have a look at us and
OL,16,Fwere jumping clear out of the water.
OL,17,FThey followed us for some of the way
OL,18,Fhome, too."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
