PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783779570
OL,3,CDolphins join RNLI volunteers during
OL,4,Ctraining exercise
OL,6,FCrew member Ian Kirkham added: "It was
OL,7,Fsuperb to watch how they effortlessly
OL,8,Frode our bow wave and the boat's wake.
OL,10,FI had to remember to keep a lookout as
OL,11,Fwell as watch the dolphins!"
OL,13,FLittlehampton RNLI is manned entirely
OL,14,Fby volunteers, who save lives at sea
OL,15,Falong the West Sussex coast between
OL,16,FWorthing and Bognor Regis.
OL,18,FThe crew train every Thursday evening
OL,19,Fand Sunday morning and were called
OL,20,Finto action 77 times in 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
